headline: Notable Raises $6M Series A to Lead Pay-at-Close Lending and Transform the Home Sale Experience
summary: Notable, the market leader in pay-at-close financing for home sale prep, today announced it raised a $6 million Series A funding round led by W. R. Berkley Corporation, with participation from Second Century Ventures. As part of the investment, Clare Tokheim of W. R. Berkley Corporation will join Notable's Board of Directors.
